column5: Hi All, Had a few hours to kill yesterday afternoon so took off locally for crappie and walleye. The crappie were small, looks like the 'famous' spot next to the ice road is getting fished out. I then headed down the skidoo trails for some walleye. Mission was a success!VIDEOhttps://youtu.be/QANXcftsenE
I always watch your videos. My 6 year old also enjoys watching them with me.
